dev-master.name: groupdocs/groupdocs-annotation
dev-master.description: Annotate PDF, Word, Excel, or image files online with GroupDocs.Annotation from your SilverStripe websites. GroupDocs.Annotation is a web-based app for sharing and annotating documents. Invite colleagues to review documents and collaborate in real-time. Add comments, exchange ideas, and resolve conflicts. Speed up the review cycle and improve communication channel between teams with GroupDocs.Annotation.
